doi:10.1017/CBO9780511497223</li>

<li>Spade, Paul Vincent, 1974, &ldquo;Ockham on Self-Reference&rdquo;,
<em>Notre Dame Journal of Formal Logic</em>, 15(2): 298&ndash;300.
doi:10.1305/ndjfl/1093891306</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1975, &ldquo;Ockham&rsquo;s Distinctions
between Absolute and Connotative Terms&rdquo;, <em>Vivarium</em>,
13(1): 55&ndash;76. doi:10.1163/156853475X00033</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1980, &ldquo;Synonymy and Equivocation in
Ockham&rsquo;s Mental Language&rdquo;, <em>Journal of the History of
