<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1990, &ldquo;Ockham, Adams and Connotation:
A Critical Notice of Marilyn Adams, William Ockham&rdquo;, <em>The
Philosophical Review</em>, 99(4): 593&ndash;612.
doi:10.2307/2185618</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1998, &ldquo;Three Versions of
Ockham&rsquo;s Reductionist Program&rdquo;, <em>Franciscan
