<li id="Spade1999">&ndash;&ndash;&ndash; (ed.), 1999a, <em>The
Cambridge Companion to Ockham</em> (Cambridge Companions to
Philosophy), Cambridge, UK/New York: Cambridge University Press.
doi:10.1017/CCOL052158244X</li>

