 <a href="#Spade1999">Spade 1999a</a>:
 1&ndash;16. doi:10.1017/CCOL052158244X.001</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1999c, &ldquo;Ockhams&rsquo; Nominalist
Metaphysics: Some Main Themes&rdquo;, in
 <a href="#Spade1999">Spade 1999a</a>:
 100&ndash;117 (ch. 5). doi:10.1017/CCOL052158244X.006</li>

<li>Stump, Eleonore, 1999, &ldquo;The Mechanisms of Cognition: Ockham
on Mediating Species&rdquo;, in
 <a href="#Spade1999">Spade 1999a</a>:
 168&ndash;203 (ch. 8). doi:10.1017/CCOL052158244X.009</li>

<li>Tachau, Katherine H., 1988, <em>Vision and Certitude in the Age of
Ockham: Optics, Epistemology, and the Foundations of Semantics,
