doi:10.1163/9789004451728</li>

<li>Trentman, John, 1970, &ldquo;Ockham on Mental&rdquo;,
<em>Mind</em>, 79(316): 586&ndash;590.
doi:10.1093/mind/LXXIX.316.586</li>

<li>Tweedale, Martin M., 1992, &ldquo;Ockham&rsquo;s Supposed
